<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA22">
<l>kālē potattirintu kattuva rāmiṉanāṇ</l>
<l>mālār kuṭipukuntā reṉmaṉattē mēlā</l>
<l>ṟarukkumiṭam pāṭṭiṉōṭum valviṉaiyār tāmvīṟ</l>
<l>ṟirukkumiṭaṅ kāṇā tiḷaittu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Such are the days that they wander about, for [their] feet to be perforated, [and] cry</l>
<l>– Māl has entered my mind as an abode – growing weary</l>
<l>without seeing a place where those with harsh deeds would sit in disctinction</l>
<l> with the expansiveness they prided themselves in before.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
